Package noteApp.view

Class FontStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • noteApp.view.FontStyle
  • public class FontStyle
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to store font styling information. Style is added to element via toCss() method which returns a valid CSS string according to values set from the ui.
    Author:
    Matias Vainio
